                    <h5 style="color:#ffffff;background-color:#ffffff;"><strong><span style="color:#313140;font-size:15pt;">14. Right to Contact a Data Protection Authority</span></strong></h5>
                    <p style="color:#ffffff;background-color:#ffffff;"><span style="color:#515164;font-size:10.5pt;">If you have a concern about how we collect and use information, please contact us. You also have the right to contact your local Data Protection Authority.&nbsp;</span></p>
